{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FileReader.readAsDataURL()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsDataURL","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_API\">File API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/FileReader\"><code>FileReader()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\"><code>readyState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\"><code>result</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort\"><code>abort()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsArrayBuffer\"><code>readAsArrayBuffer()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsBinaryString\"><code>readAsBinaryString()</code></a></li><li><em><code>readAsDataURL()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText\"><code>readAsText()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort_event\"><code>abort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/load_event\"><code>load</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadend_event\"><code>loadend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadstart_event\"><code>loadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/progress_event\"><code>progress</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a File API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURl\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>O método <code>readAsDataURL é usado para ler o conteúdo do tipo&nbsp;</code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a>.<br>\n Quando a operação de leitura acaba, a flag&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\"><code>readyState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> muda para <strong>DONE</strong>&nbsp;e o evento&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">loadend (en-US)</a></code> é disparado.<br>\n Então o&nbsp;atributo&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\"><code>result</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> irá conter a URL codificada&nbsp;em&nbsp;base64 do arquivo.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><em>instanceOfFileReader</em>.readAsDataURL(blob);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametros","title":"Parametros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"blob\"><code>blob</code></dt>\n <dd>O conteúdo do tipo <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> ou&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> que queremos ler.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">&lt;input type=\"file\" onchange=\"previewFile()\"&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n&lt;img src=\"\" height=\"200\" alt=\"Prévia da imagem...\"&gt;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">function previewFile() {\n  var preview = document.querySelector('img');\n  var file    = document.querySelector('input[type=file]').files[0];\n  var reader  = new FileReader();\n\n  reader.onloadend = function () {\n    preview.src = reader.result;\n  }\n\n  if (file) {\n    reader.readAsDataURL(file);\n  } else {\n    preview.src = \"\";\n  }\n}</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"demo","title":"Demo","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"100%\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsDataURL/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo_de_leitura_com_múltiplos_arquivos","title":"Exemplo de leitura com múltiplos arquivos","isH3":false,"content":"<h4 id=\"html_2\"><strong>HTML</strong></h4>\n\n<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>&lt;input id=\"browse\" type=\"file\" onchange=\"previewFiles()\" multiple&gt;\n&lt;div id=\"preview\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"javascript_2\">JavaScript</h4>\n\n<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>function previewFiles() {\n\n  var preview = document.querySelector('#preview');\n  var files   = document.querySelector('input[type=file]').files;\n\n  function readAndPreview(file) {\n\n    // Make sure `file.name` matches our extensions criteria\n    if ( /\\.(jpe?g|png|gif)$/i.test(file.name) ) {\n      var reader = new FileReader();\n\n      reader.addEventListener(\"load\", function () {\n        var image = new Image();\n        image.height = 100;\n        image.title = file.name;\n        image.src = this.result;\n        preview.appendChild( image );\n      }, false);\n\n      reader.readAsDataURL(file);\n    }\n\n  }\n\n  if (files) {\n    [].forEach.call(files, readAndPreview);\n  }\n\n}</code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\"><strong>Nota:</strong>&nbsp;O construtor do&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader()</code></a>&nbsp;não é suportado &nbsp;por versões anteriores à 10 do&nbsp;Internet Explorer. Para uma maior compatibilidade você pode ver os exemplos <a class=\"internal external\" href=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/3699/crossbrowser_image_preview.html\" title=\"crossbrowser_image_preview.html\" rel=\" noopener\">prévia de imagem básica</a>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/3698/image_upload_preview.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">prévia de imagem avançada</a>.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<p>{{page(\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader\",\"Specifications\")}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility_2","title":"Compatibilidade","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div><div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p><div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer*</th>\n   <th>Opera*</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3.6\" title=\"Released on 2010-01-21.\">3.6</a> (1.9.2)</td>\n   <td>7</td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td>12.02</td>\n   <td>6.0.2</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div><div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>32</td>\n   <td>3</td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td>11.5</td>\n   <td>6.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas_de_implementações","title":"Notas de implementações","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>IE9 possui uma&nbsp;<a href=\"http://html5labs.interoperabilitybridges.com/prototypes/fileapi/fileapi/info\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">File API Lab</a>.</li>\n <li>Opera possui&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.opera.com/docs/specs/presto28/file/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">suporte parcial</a>&nbsp;na versão 11.1.</li>\n</ul><h4 id=\"notas_específicas_para_gecko\">Notas específicas para Gecko</h4><ul>\n <li>Em versões anteriores ao Gecko 2.0 beta 7 (Firefox 4.0 beta 7), todos os parâmetros&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> abaixo eram parâmetros <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a>. Isto foi então atualizado para adequarem-se corretamente às especificações.</li>\n <li>Em versões anteriores ao Gecko 13.0 (Firefox 13.0 / Thunderbird 13.0 / SeaMonkey 2.10), a propriedade&nbsp;<code>FileReader.error</code>&nbsp;retornava um objeto&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>FileError</code></a>. Esta interface foi removida e a propriedade <code>FileReader.error</code>&nbsp;agora retorna o objeto&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, assim como está definido na última versão da FileAPI.</li>\n</ul><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Exemplo de leitura com múltiplos arquivos","id":"exemplo_de_leitura_com_múltiplos_arquivos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Compatibilidade","id":"browser_compatibility_2"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O método readAsDataURL é usado para ler o conteúdo do tipo Blob ou File.\n Quando a operação de leitura acaba, a flag readyState (en-US) muda para DONE e o evento loadend (en-US) é disparado.\n Então o atributo result (en-US) irá conter a URL codificada em base64 do arquivo.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FileReader.readAsDataURL()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsDataURL()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsDataURL()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsDataURL()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsDataURL()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsDataURL()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"FileReader.readAsDataURL()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/filereader/readasdataurl","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/filereader/readasdataurl/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader","title":"FileReader"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsDataURL","title":"FileReader.readAsDataURL()"}],"pageTitle":"FileReader.readAsDataURL() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}